T1  - The relationship between short interest and stock returns in the Canadian market
AU  - Ackert, Lucy F.
AU  - Athanassakos, George
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 29
IS  - 7
SP  - 1729
EP  - 1749
